parameters.name: AclEntryComment
parameters.description:
The remarks of the ACL rule.

It must be 2 to 100 characters in length, and can contain digits, underscores (\_), and hyphens (-). It must start with a letter.

parameters.name: AclEntryId
parameters.description: The ID of the ACL rule to which the IP entry belongs.

parameters.name: AclId
parameters.description: The ID of the ACL to which the IP entry belongs.
